{"tid":438652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一地兩檢】民主派斥抽議程改審無約束力議案損互信　玩弄議會運作","createTime":"2017-10-17T06:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T07:50:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"43ba7a78b96e0479c1a934e29f15f1f46652b141","tid":438652,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T06:29:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/232231/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E6%96%A5%E6%8A%BD%E8%AD%B0%E7%A8%8B%E6%94%B9%E5%AF%A9%E7%84%A1%E7%B4%84%E6%9D%9F%E5%8A%9B%E8%AD%B0%E6%A1%88%E6%90%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F232231%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%258A%25BD%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%259D%259F%25E5%258A%259B%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%2590%258D%2F&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a39c6b95\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/232231/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E6%96%A5%E6%8A%BD%E8%AD%B0%E7%A8%8B%E6%94%B9%E5%AF%A9%E7%84%A1%E7%B4%84%E6%9D%9F%E5%8A%9B%E8%AD%B0%E6%A1%88%E6%90%8D/</a><br />\n<br />\n【一地兩檢】民主派斥抽議程改審無約束力議案損互信　玩弄議會運作<br />\n 2017-10-17 12:31字體： A A A<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今早出席行會前表示，由於時間緊迫，運輸及房屋局局長陳帆明日將於立法會大會上，提出中止已進入委員會審議階段的《2017年印花稅(修訂)條例草案》辯論，以確保政府就「一地兩檢」提出的無約束力議案能如期在下周三（25日）進行。<br />\n<br />\n民主派會議召集人莫乃光指，民主派對此強烈譴責，批評政府聯合建制利用議事規則來玩弄議會運作，嚴重損害特首和他們之間的互信，反映林鄭無心與民主派修補關係。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/17121008/image1508212885085.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F17121008%2Fimage1508212885085.png&h=ac273409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片